fingerprints all over it.

649
00:34:59,330 --> 00:35:00,854
His Master's Voice.

650
00:35:00,965 --> 00:35:02,592
Also not mine.

651
00:35:02,700 --> 00:35:04,167
Pleasure to meet you, Mr. Smith.

652
00:35:04,268 --> 00:35:05,530
Smitty. Kurt.

653
00:35:05,636 --> 00:35:08,400
We have the same last name.
We don't want people to mix us up.

654
00:35:08,506 --> 00:35:10,701
