660
00:35:20,151 --> 00:35:21,277
Pardon?

661
00:35:21,385 --> 00:35:24,252
We'd rather people
not know we were here.

662
00:35:24,355 --> 00:35:26,414
If it gets out we're meeting...

663
00:35:26,524 --> 00:35:28,822
- Of course not.
- Yes, right.

664
00:35:28,926 --> 00:35:30,120
Bye.

665
00:35:31,362 --> 00:35:33,660
- I'll let him know she called.
- Okay.

666
00:35:35,066 --> 00:35:36,556
I like the direction you're taking.

667
00:35:36,667 --> 00:35:37,759
Good.

668
00:35:37,869 --> 00:35:40,736
Now that I've given you your babies
and your Xerox machine,

669
00:35:40,838 --> 00:35:42,499
should I throw in
a couple of elephants?

670
00:35:42,607 --> 00:35:44,199
I don't want there to be any excuse

671
00:35:44,308 --> 00:35:45,707
when you can't bring in
Martinson's Coffee.

672
00:35:45,810 --> 00:35:48,040
Don't get worked up.

673
00:35:48,146 --> 00:35:50,137
You know, there are other ways
to think of things

674
00:35:50,248 --> 00:35:52,239
than the way you think of them.

675
00:35:59,690 --> 00:36:00,816
The testimonials.

676
00:36:00,925 --> 00:36:02,825
I was thinking we could
get younger girls.

677
00:36:02,927 --> 00:36:04,121
Sixth graders.

678
00:36:04,228 --> 00:36:05,490
It would mean different publications.

679
00:36:05,596 --> 00:36:07,063
Do they need Clearasil that early?

680
00:36:07,165 --> 00:36:08,598
- Doesn't matter.
- Doesn't.

681
00:36:08,699 --> 00:36:10,599
I guess we could try that.

682
00:36:11,636 --> 00:36:13,934
Two more from DDB.

683
00:36:14,038 --> 00:36:15,266
Even younger.

684
00:36:15,373 --> 00:36:18,274
