you handed Roger is coming in.

685
00:36:18,376 --> 00:36:19,434
You're an idiot.

686
00:36:19,544 --> 00:36:21,512
I don't understand that. I'm only 22.

687
00:36:21,612 --> 00:36:23,409
You don't count.

688
00:36:23,514 --> 00:36:25,072
We've got to get him out of here.

689
00:36:25,183 --> 00:36:26,275
Come on, Daddy.

690
00:36:26,384 --> 00:36:28,818
How often do you get to celebrate
getting some girl pregnant?

691
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:30,512
Campbell, you're buying.

692
00:36:30,621 --> 00:36:32,452
We still have to show
Mohawk to Mr. Draper.

693
00:36:32,557 --> 00:36:33,717
Dale's not here.

694
00:36:33,824 --> 00:36:35,223
