695
00:36:40,064 --> 00:36:43,500
Kids. What's the big deal?

696
00:36:43,601 --> 00:36:45,125
Do you want to have kids?

697
00:36:46,737 --> 00:36:48,830
Eventually.

698
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:50,373
Exactly.

699
00:37:01,552 --> 00:37:03,645
Mr. Romano, Miss Olson.

700
00:37:05,223 --> 00:37:06,520
Send them in.

701
00:37:08,926 --> 00:37:10,223
Where are we?

702
00:37:10,328 --> 00:37:12,125
You tell us.

703
00:37:14,565 --> 00:37:16,499
"Where are you going?"

704
00:37:18,603 --> 00:37:20,468
